By: Sri Chandrasekhara Bhâratî Swâmigal
---
What is it that accompanies us when we pass off from this body? Wealth
and other things remain behind in the house itself. Friends and
relatives come as far as the burning ground and return home from
there. Only the good deeds and the evil ones done by us go with us
when we go.
